<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CSE Coding Hub | Sathish Yadav</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/a076d05399.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <style>
        body { background-color: #f4f7f6; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; }
        .hero-section { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3c72 0%, #2a5298 100%); color: white; padding: 60px 0; text-align: center; }
        .card { border: none; transition: 0.3s; border-radius: 15px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .card:hover { transform: translateY(-10px); }
        .btn-custom { background-color: #ff4b2b; color: white; border-radius: 25px; padding: 10px 25px; text-decoration: none; }
        .btn-custom:hover { background-color: #ff416c; color: white; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="hero-section">
        <h1>CSE CODING HUB</h1>
        <p>Master Coding with Sathish Yadav's Curated Resources</p>
    </div>

    <div class="container my-5">
        <div class="row g-4">
            
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card p-4 text-center">
                    <h3>Python</h3>
                    <p>The best language for Data Science & AI.</p>
                    <a href="https://www.w3schools.com/python/" target="_blank" class="btn-custom">Start Learning</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card p-4 text-center">
                    <h3>Java</h3>
                    <p>Foundation for Android & Enterprise apps.</p>
                    <a href="https://www.javatpoint.com/java-tutorial" target="_blank" class="btn-custom">Learn Java</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card p-4 text-center">
                    <h3>Data Structures</h3>
                    <p>The most important topic for Placements.</p>
                    <a href="https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/data-structures/" target="_blank" class="btn-custom">Go to DSA</a>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

        <div class="mt-5 p-5 bg-white rounded shadow-sm text-center">
            <h2>Practice Coding</h2>
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-3 mt-3">
                <a href="https://leetcode.com/" class="btn btn-outline-primary">LeetCode</a>
                <a href="https://www.hackerrank.com/" class="btn btn-outline-success">HackerRank</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="text-center py-4 text-muted">
        &copy; 2026 Designed by Sathish Yadav
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
